<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA37">
<l>iruntaṇ kamalat tirumalari ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>tiruntu ticaimukaṉait tantāy – poruntiyaniṉ</l>
<l>pātaṅka ḷēttip paṇiyāvēṟ palpiṟappu</l>
<l>mētaṅka ḷellā memakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who gave [the world] him with perfect faces in [all the four] directions,</l>
<l>in the brilliant blossom of the big cool lotus, if we do not</l>
<l>befittingly praise your feet [and] humble ourselves, for many births</l>
<l>we [shall] have all afflictions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
